thread.title: Neville H
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Neville H

author: Neville H
title: Neville H
text: We recently purchased a four pack of toner cartridges for our brother printer. I ordered at 11pm and they were delivered the next day. They fitted in and worked perfectly. Individually they retail at office works for $109 and I paid $129 for the four. A bargain and great service and a great product.
